# Tiles Rules (Rendering Layer)

## Purpose
Provide map rendering data.

## Components
- PMTiles → static tiles
- Martin → dynamic tiles
- style.json → map style

## Rules
- Tiles are for rendering only
- Do NOT store business data here
- Do NOT connect API to tile generation

## PMTiles
- Prebuilt using Planetiler/Tippecanoe
- Stored in R2/CDN

## Martin
- Reads from PostGIS
- Generates tiles dynamically

## Style
- Use MapLibre style spec
- Keep layers minimal

## Forbidden
- No API logic
- No database writes